## ğŸ” Authentication Methods

| Method     | Description                                                                     |
| ---------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `password` | Standard login using email and password (supports app-specific passwords).      |
| `oauth2`   | Secure OAuth2 token authentication â€” required for Gmail and Microsoft accounts. |

